            {
                "heading": "Meter",
                "body": "A relic from the days of yore, this tag group is now unused, replaced by unit_hud_interface.\n\nDespite being totally obsolete and only serving to take up precious space in tag data for absolutely no benefit whatsoever, it continues to endure in many a globals tag to this very day, annoying and confusing modders for decades.\n\nWe should all strive to be like the meter tag: to never give up even when everyone else has given up on you.",
